v 3
d 'DUMMIFY': module to create indicator variables with automatic labels
d
d {cmd:dummify} creates a set of indicator variables from a categorical
d variable with non-negative integer values, one per level, and automatically
d labels them in the form of "variable label = value label". It is essentially
d a more convenient implementation of tab, gen().
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260610
d
d Author: Gorkem Aksaray, Trinity College Dublin
d Support: aksarayg@tcd.ie
d
f dummify.ado
